title: Mini-Ep 263: Ye (The) Olde Podcast
itunes:title: Mini-Ep 263: Ye (The) Olde Podcast
description:
Kate and Doree reminisce over the cultural zeitgeist that was (and is) The Real Housewives and hear from listeners with recommendations for the husband with extreme eczema, about being scared to be a mother, and with a fun language lesson!
